    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOU ARE WHAT YOU EAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In <i>Clover's Quadrants</i>, your four directions of movement correspond with four different inventory slots: Up, down, left, and right. Pick up an item on your left side, and now that item's ability will be used every time you move left! This simple premise is explored in depth, with many items and mechanical surprises to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Clover's Quadrants</i> aims to be a difficult-but-fair experience. Players less experienced with Sokoban puzzles should expect a challenge! If you <i>are</i> a more seasoned puzzler, don't expect a cakewalk either.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191170/extras/51fee4fcf21f9b324532fcf093c5bb6f.poster.avif?t=1772067216\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191170/extras/51fee4fcf21f9b324532fcf093c5bb6f.webm?t=1772067216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191170/extras/51fee4fcf21f9b324532fcf093c5bb6f.mp4?t=1772067216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~100 puzzles with a wide range of difficulty</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bespoke art for every puzzle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visual hints for every puzzle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Free Play&quot; option to unlock all puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus &quot;cut content&quot; puzzles</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorblind accessible by default</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191170/extras/1a9ad018d7e54f0c1d1e2ca421292e8e.poster.avif?t=1772067216\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191170/extras/1a9ad018d7e54f0c1d1e2ca421292e8e.webm?t=1772067216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191170/extras/1a9ad018d7e54f0c1d1e2ca421292e8e.mp4?t=1772067216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT ABOUT UDLR_MODIFY?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>UDLR_Modify</i> was originally created for the Acerola Jam 0 as a prototype with 20 puzzles, where it was among the most popular  games submitted. <i>Clover's Quadrants</i> is the full-length follow up to that game, keeping the best puzzles from the original while adding many more, adding new item types, and modifying some of the base mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191170/extras/ccd9aad1329926bb5aaa3fa1f00cee29.poster.avif?t=1772067216\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191170/extras/ccd9aad1329926bb5aaa3fa1f00cee29.webm?t=1772067216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191170/extras/ccd9aad1329926bb5aaa3fa1f00cee29.mp4?t=1772067216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
